            "text": {
              "status": "generated",
              "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Annotation</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><tr><th>Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us</th></tr><tr><td>All hematological parameters are within normal limits except for mildly elevated mean platelet volume (MPV) and platelet distribution width (PDW), which may indicate increased platelet turnover or activation. No evidence of anemia, leukocytosis, or thrombocytopenia. Correlate with clinical context; if asymptomatic, these findings are likely of no immediate concern but may warrant monitoring.</td></tr></table></div>"
